<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 2820/98 of 21 December 1998 applying a multiannual scheme of generalised tariff preferences for the period 1 July 1999 to 31 December 2001(1), as last amended by Commission Regulation (EC) No 1310/2000(2), and in particular Article 13(1) thereof, </inglise>
